name: Naboo Celebration
Lore: 'The heroic actions of Amidala''s forces and Boss Nass'' army saved Naboo from the Trade Federation. Definitely a cause for celebration!',
Text: 'Deploy on table. If Amidala at a Theed Palace site (or Boss Nass at an exterior Naboo site), opponent''s cards with ability deploy +2 there. Once during battle at a Naboo site, if you just drew a Gungan or Royal Naboo Security for battle destiny, opponent loses 1 Force.',
